    "description": "Shin galaxy: Alpha War is a space shooter with some RPG mechanics, where the player can improve the attributes of each space ship. In addition, the player will be able to count on other space ships, which will have unique stats. The game has more than 70 stages, content to unlock, boss battles, 15 ships and 85 missions to complete. There is also infinite mode to test your survival skills.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Laser Shot</strong></li></ul>The common ship shot, simply hit it on enemy ships and you will be good.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/80f034d84d9c1e32f15051f2159f2cab.poster.avif?t=1695646636\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/80f034d84d9c1e32f15051f2159f2cab.webm?t=1695646636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/80f034d84d9c1e32f15051f2159f2cab.mp4?t=1695646636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Charged Shot</strong></li></ul>The shot with immense damage per second potential, however, needs to be charged before it can be fired. The projectile passes through enemies with incredible speed.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/451894a5274290e18a7c487d8a2de4eb.poster.avif?t=1695646636\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/451894a5274290e18a7c487d8a2de4eb.webm?t=1695646636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/451894a5274290e18a7c487d8a2de4eb.mp4?t=1695646636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Bomb</strong></li></ul>The bomb is a projectile that does high single damage on hit and will do AoE damage on explosion. Can also destroy certain objects.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/e6c7cf7c8d0dad4662a2160edc687d33.poster.avif?t=1695646636\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/e6c7cf7c8d0dad4662a2160edc687d33.webm?t=1695646636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/e6c7cf7c8d0dad4662a2160edc687d33.mp4?t=1695646636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ships</strong></h2><br>The ships available for use were created using geometric shapes, each one has its own particularity, as well as an improved version.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Ignis Series</strong></li></ul>This model has its stats balanced, which facilitates combat in Shin Galaxy.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/2916058620fc9b9abd152efd7bdc7145.avif?t=1695646636\" width=373 height=115 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Aqua Series</strong></li></ul>This model stands out in its fire rate, on the other hand, it is very sensitive.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/426c79b7c94c168080a3560393abae5c.avif?t=1695646636\" width=373 height=115 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Terra Series</strong></li></ul>This model has the highest attack power among the other spaceships, however, it has low locomotion speed.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/1e59f95d8c390dbf4d8c0a3832d48199.avif?t=1695646636\" width=373 height=115 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Tonitruum Series</strong></li></ul>This model is the one with the highest speed of locomotion, however, it has the lowest bomb capacity.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/144214379e2be7dc2a2fe29699dc1937.avif?t=1695646636\" width=373 height=115 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Tenebris Series</strong></li></ul><br>This model has the greatest survivability and has a lot of life, but the rate of fire is low.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/1da9d520faccc36b78390ed2f335af8b.avif?t=1695646636\" width=373 height=115 /></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improving spaceships</h2></strong><br><br>Each ship has 08 attributes that can be improved with crystals in the Hangar, they are:<br><br> - Attack<br> - Elemental Attack<br> - Speed<br> - Fire Rate<br> - Bomb Capacity<br> - Bomb Fire Rate<br> - Laser Cannons<br> - Life<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135780/extras/9f5efdc8ad90b199a28dce5801c2b867.avif?t=1695646636\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Now, go and explore the Shin Galaxy.",
